metadata.editComments: The #III chords are chromatic mediants, not really easy to convey in TheoryTab. I can't add multiple voices, so I just chose the prominent one. From the multi-platform 3rd person shooter Bionicle Heroes by Traveller's Tale.
Added bridge. The key keeps jumping all over the place because these chromatic mediants make it so easy to establish a new key center. Just move from one chromatic mediant to a different one.
